Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 03,06,2024

Introduction

Welcome to Danoaesthetics ("we", "our", "us"). We are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our app, Danoaesthetics ("App").

Information Collection

We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: When you use our App, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and other contact details.
Usage Data: We collect information about how you use our App, including your IP address, device information, and operating system.
Use of Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To Provide and Maintain Our App: We use your information to provide and maintain the App's functionality.
To Improve Our App: We analyze the usage data to improve our App's performance and user experience.
To Communicate with You: We may use your contact information to send you updates and respond to your inquiries.
Data Sharing

We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following cases:

With Your Consent: We may share your information with third parties if you have given us your explicit consent.
For Legal Reasons: We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our legal rights.
User Rights

You have the right to access, update, and delete your personal information. You can do this by contacting us at [Your Contact Email].

Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at Danoaesthetics@gmail.com.
